{"tid":1773080,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"靠攏黃色經濟百利而無一害，點解咁少店藍轉黃","createTime":"2019-12-07T07:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T08:18:26.000Z","uid":111253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e626448e87876e43020aafdc63985f50bf0460f6","tid":1773080,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"其實冇出賣手足，藍轉黃係可以歡迎，唔理佢真唔真心<br />\n果啲唔係藍到發黑，死唔轉黃嘅店，<br />\n奶共共產黨唔會俾錢你洗，個朵又臭，仲隨時俾人裝修<br />\n反而轉黃生意一定爆升，<br />\n香港人乜都冇最多就係錢，仲可以企道德高地<br />\n諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633d88d846bee8a5b41101299593ba1fabff053b","tid":1773080,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.